{"tid":1967185,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"搵錢容乜易 （傻淡勿入）","createTime":"2020-04-10T17:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T10:07:16.000Z","uid":89349,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f99e3dcaf0ea8050c5c2d9081529cd6107aec442","tid":1967185,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnWvbNt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnWvbNt.png&h=1e7a809a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加入警隊，實踐抱負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cec6781183c9103b72706651179deac3769dedab","tid":1967185,"uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T17:16:33.000Z","msg":"去年十月，陳小姐坐巴士回家途中，巴士被警方截停，所有人須下車搜身。陳小姐指，當時女警要求她在其他男警及乘客前脫去連身裙。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐之後向投訴警察課投訴該名女警。陳小姐指，警方當晚有拍攝片段，故按《私隱條例》，向警方申請索取涉及她的個人資料，惟警方指片段亦涉及其他人的資料，拒絕她的申請。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳小姐之後向警方指明，可以申請遮蓋其他個人資料的片段，陳小姐引述警方口頭說法，指警務處沒有軟件可以「打格」，如陳小姐仍須索取片段，須支付購置電腦軟件，以及警員為片段「打格」所涉工時的工資。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n陳小姐要求警方白紙黑字，列出須付費項目及費用，以及軟件的報價單，警方一直沒有回覆，直至一個月後，警方以片段涉及刑事調查，拒絕陳小姐申請。<br />\n<br />\n警方回應查詢時指，警方根據《私隱條例》有權收取費用。<br />\n<br />\n至於警方曾經上載過「打格」片段，為何涉事警員指警務處沒有這類軟件？<br />\n<br />\n警方回應指，事件中警員的電腦，並未配備相關軟件。<br />\n<br />\n又指有關電子紀錄涉及一宗刑事案件，該案件仍在調查中，警方不作進一步評論，會按《私隱條例》處理事主申請。<br />\n<br />\n私隱專員公署指，已經接到事主的投訴，因此不會評論個案，但指一般而言資料使用者只可收取「直接有關及必需」的費用。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520003-20200410.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520003-20200410.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VUZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=df0d03a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520003-20200410.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=47f5c4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520003-20200410.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"57b7dc284095e08f4ada7f1c55222f53768d7361","tid":1967185,"uid":210363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家 死完爸爸死媽媽"},{"pid":"e6826fcef43912bc4387becda04d9f8decfc66bc","tid":1967185,"uid":89349,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQSc9Lf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQSc9Lf.jpg&h=82922d46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d5882f3118cbea4f3eb133f2aaab9d57098a109","tid":1967185,"uid":89349,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57b7dc284095e08f4ada7f1c55222f53768d7361","tid":1967185,"uid":210363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家 死完爸爸死媽媽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"死埋仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93091b235ee531e8b21b823f3044358b47c8296f","tid":1967185,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"死埋女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /